{"tid":2423559,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"沽空機構香櫞：GameStop應收購電子競技娛樂　改變營運情況","createTime":"2021-02-26T03:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T07:27:28.000Z","uid":120499,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cad3bb0d818f317a37ccd55fe4218b8a14b00bf8","tid":2423559,"uid":120499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:36:20.000Z","msg":"在遊戲驛站GameStop（GME）「散戶打大鱷」一戰中「敗走」的沽空機構香櫞（Citron）發表報告指，GameStop應該收購電子競技娛樂（Esports Entertainmen，GMBL），掌握消費者最愛的遊戲與博弈，以改變其現時營運情況。<br />\n<br />\n香櫞研究創辦人 Andrew Left 指出，「我們在GameStop上學到兩個簡單的知識：人們喜歡遊戲，也喜歡賭博」。Left表示，GameStop可以收購電子競技娛樂，吸引數百萬新客戶，並將其客群導流至電競下注平台，同時又可以透過客戶數據庫獲利。<br />\n<br />\nLeft認為，GameStop是現時市場新寵兒，可以集資並重新成為市場強勢參與者，預計其市值介乎80億至100億美元之間。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1614307774401&amp;issue=20210226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1614307774401%26issue%3D20210226&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6%2BPMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=c7a15617\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1614307774401&amp;issue=20210226</a><br />\n阿婆走得快，轉性了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2969e2c03f6180bd0fb6b00c1666bbb6862f1daa","tid":2423559,"uid":120499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T05:56:18.000Z","msg":"pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861d9e46088ace553d57851f76a9a9987bdb1119","tid":2423559,"uid":54959,"like":2,"dislike"